summary:
DESCRIPTION for Food Fight Mod:

This simple CHEAT Mod adds several food items as ammo for your bow. Buy them at Belethor\'s General Goods in Whiterun. Be careful of explosions! (on impact).  

M7 1-15-2013. 

ver.1.0
